N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 810.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

The Frank C. Moore local government achievement awards are
hereby established in order to honor Frank C. Moore for his lasting
contributions to the strengthening of local government in New York State and to
recognize local governments which have taken outstanding action to meet the
needs of their citizens through more effective services. Notes
